{"title_page": "Sumbul Iqbal", "text_new": "{{Short description|Pakistani actress}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name          = Sumbul Iqbal\n| image         = Sumbul Iqbal.jpg\n| alt           = \n| caption       = \n| birth_name    = Sumbul Iqbal Khan\n| birth_date    = {{birth date|df=y|1981|8|30}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.stylefigures.com/sumbul-iqbal-dramas-wedding-plan-pics-profile|last=Fallon|first=Justine|title=Sumbul Iqbal dramas, wedding plan, pics & profile|date=4 November 2014|website=Style Figures|accessdate=16 October 2019}}</ref>\n| birth_place   = Karachi\n| death_date    = <!-- {{Death date and age|YYYY|MM|DD|YYYY|MM|DD}} or {{Death-date and age|Month DD, YYYY|Month DD, YYYY}} (death date then birth date) -->\n| death         = \n| years_active  = 2011\u2013present\n| nationality   = \n| other_names   = \n| occupation    = [[Actress]], [[Model (profession)|Model]]\n| relatives     = Komal Iqbal (sister)\n| known_for     = \n| notable_works = \n| awards        =\n}}\n\n'''Sumbul Iqbal''' ({{Nastaliq|\u0633\u0646\u0628\u0644 \u0627\u0642\u0628\u0627\u0644}}) is a Pakistani television actress.<ref name=f47>{{cite web|title=Sumbul Iqbal, a fresh face in showbiz industry of Pakistan|url=http://www.fashion47.pk/birthday-calendar/sumbul-iqbal/|publisher=fashion47.pk|access-date=March 11, 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130301105053/http://www.fashion47.pk/birthday-calendar/sumbul-iqbal/|archive-date=March 1, 2013|url-status=dead|df=mdy-all}}</ref> She is best known for her leading roles in ''[[Meray Khwab Raiza Raiza]]'' (2011), ''[[Kis Din Mera Viyah Howay Ga|Kis Din Mera Viyah Howay Ga 2]]'' (2012), ''[[Raju Rocket]]'' (2012), ''[[Rukhsaar (TV series)|Rukhsaar]]'' (2013)'', [[Aik Pal]]'' (2014)'', [[Tumse Mil Kay|Tumsay Mil Kay]]'' (2015)'', [[Aik Thi Rania]]'' (2017)''.''<ref name=\"gohar\">{{Cite web|url=http://images.dawn.com/news/1174011|title=Drama Neelum Kinarey highlights the hidden beauty of Kashmir: Gohar Mumtaz|last=Haq|first=Images Staff {{!}} Irfan Ul|date=2015-10-10|website=DAWN|language=en|archive-url=|archive-date=|url-status=|access-date=2019-01-17}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hipinpakistan.com/news/1148061|title=Sumbul Iqbal shines as a Kashmiri beauty in \u2018Neelum Kinarey\u2019|last=Jawaid|first=Wajiha|date=2015-10-08|website=HIP|language=en|access-date=2019-01-17}}</ref> Iqbal was last seen in a role of Isha in [[Hum TV]]'s ''[[Jaal (TV series)|Jaal]]'' (2019).\n\n== Life and career ==\nSumbul Iqbal Khan was born in [[Karachi]], [[Sindh]]. [[ARY Digital]]'s she noted for playing variety of characters in dramas , series ''Roag'' (2011),<ref name=roag/> which was one of the highest rated Urdu series of 2011.{{citation needed|date=March 2019}} She later appeared in [[Hum TV]]'s [[Meray Khwab Raiza Raiza|''Mere'' ''Khwab'' ''Raiza'' ''Raiza'']] (2012) opposite [[Syed Jibran]].\n\n== Filmography ==\n\n=== Television ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year !! Title!! Role!! Notes\n|-\n|2011|| ''Buri Aurat''||Aleena|| \n|-\n|2011|| ''Dil e Abad''||Rubi||\n|-\n|2011||''Roag''||Nimra||\n<ref name=roag>{{Cite web|url=http://images.dawn.com/news/1176410|title=10 iconic Pakistani TV dramas you should binge-watch this weekend|last=Haider|first=Sadaf|date=2016-10-21|website=Images|language=en|access-date=2019-01-17}}</ref>\n|-\n|2011|| ''[[Meray Khwab Raiza Raiza]]''|| Zainab|| \n|-\n|2011|| ''My Dear Sautan''||Tehzeeb||\n|-\n|2011|| ''Sabz Qadam ''||Momina||\n|-\n|2011|| ''[[Kis Din Mera Viyah Howay Ga|Kis Din Mera Viyah Howay Ga 2]]''||Naik Parveen|| \n|-\n|2012 ||''[[Kitni Girhain Baaki Hain]]'' || || Episode 10\n|-\n|2012|| ''[[Raju Rocket]]''||Hina||[[Hum Award for Best Soap Actress]]\n|-\n|2013|| ''[[Teri Berukhi (Geo TV)|Teri Berukhi]]''|| || \n|-\n|2013|| ''[[Rukhsaar (TV series)|Rukhsaar]]''||Rukhsaar||\n|-\n|2013|| ''[[Shareek-e-Hayat]]''||Hina||Anthology series\n|-\n|2013|| ''Shab e Zindagi  ''|| Mariyam || \n|-\n|2013|| ''[[Rasam (Geo TV)|Rasam]]''|| Amber ||\n|-\n|2013|| '